meta {
  name: Get Light Client Updates
  type: http
  seq: 2
}

get {
  url: https://eth-mainnetbeacon.g.alchemy.com/v2/{{api_key}}/eth/v1/beacon/light_client/updates
  body: none
  auth: none
}

params:query {
  start_period: 1
  count: 1
}

docs {
  ## Get Light Client Updates

  Returns the light client update objects for the given sync committee period range. Each update contains information needed to advance a light client's state.

  ### Query Parameters
  - `start_period` (required): The sync committee period to start from
  - `count` (required): The number of periods to return

